text: Alf Nørgaard (30 October 1916 - 15 September 1971) was a Norwegian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1916 births Category:1971 deaths Category:Norwegian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Norway Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:People from Sauda
